{
  "stem": "3100.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I arranged, I wanted to take my wife with me, and those two girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Either they all go, or none of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I arranged to take them all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we legally left the camp to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We reached the city of Lodz, and my wife said she's getting off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, at that time she wasn't my wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She's going to go back to the place where she was born.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was going to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See if she can find anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to see if she could find anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, later on I found out that she came back to Elblag, where there were people, and she couldn't find anybody.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the janitor said, oh, you know, he thought she came back from the other world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I've been back to Krashnik, to my town with my brother, and I could not find anybody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So while we went back to Krashnik, we found out that there was a girl that know-- knew, that was in camp together with my wife.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she escaped somehow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she already married there a fellow from Krashnik, a lonsman of mine-- whom I know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we got to talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told her I know a [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Parelke ?] She said, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Parelke ?] is alive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oy, would I like to see her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said I would like too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where is she?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She's in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went back for her and took her back to Krashnik.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, of course, my older brother said, if you like each other, there is no way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, no, we like each other to live like sisters and brothers-- like a sister and a brother because we didn't have anybody.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
